column9: Relates a resource (e.g., document or dataset) to a research project it is associated with.
Indicates that a claim is a literal quotation from another source item in the MemO knowledge graph.
Provides provenance for a piece of information by pointing to the source that supports it.
Links a source item to the data feed from which it was ingested.
Specifies the temporal period covered by a resource.
Points to the metadata record URL.
Points to the actual resource URL.
Specifies the type of the objects provided by the NFDI4Memory resource.
